{"tid":2234613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"14個國家受訪者均過半數對中國持負面印象","createTime":"2020-10-08T04:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T05:50:03.000Z","uid":56115,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"56862eb68721deb187dbddb7f59b8520a449cd7d","tid":2234613,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:36:26.000Z","msg":"韓國中央日報報導，美國一間民調及智庫機構（Pew Research Center）對14國家進行對中國印象的民意調查。<br />\n<br />\n多國受訪者中，日本對中持負面印象最高（８６％、其次的是瑞士（８５％）、澳洲（８１％）、韓國・丹麥（７５％ ）、英國（７４％）、美國・加拿大・荷蘭（７３％）、比利時（７１％）、法國（７０％）、西班牙（６３％）、意大利（６２％）<br />\n<br />\n「韓國・美國・英國・德國・西班牙・荷蘭・澳洲・加拿大等九個國家對中持負面印象是15年以來最高。<br />\n<br />\n今次的調查在６月１０日－８月３日期間進行，對14國家共14276人進行電話訪問。"},{"pid":"1b377443d818c8cd87d23d02ad7e21b9c1d0d0fa","tid":2234613,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:36:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.japanese.joins.com/Jarticle/270936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.japanese.joins.com%2FJarticle%2F270936&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5NjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=e8967b6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.japanese.joins.com/Jarticle/270936</a>"},{"pid":"ed049d9b204a82cf2305cf494debba05f38cde48","tid":2234613,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac023f8b124b3934319f08857c0575abadf48424","tid":2234613,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:38:24.000Z","msg":"支那：你地有誤解，歡迎你地嚟新彊認識支國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d3fa52a5d269a51c5138baaaf7f85208e483c2","tid":2234613,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb7ff5a355cff2670c09d1869801c5e57523282","tid":2234613,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-1